originalText.text: I did an EQ Assessment and Debrief with Alan Samuel Cohen and I got so much clarity about how I can leverage my strengths to achieve my goals. Alan is extremely knowledgeable and insightful when it comes to assessing the gap between where you are and where you want to go. After our call I had a renewed energy for what I am currently working on, I've been more productive in the last week than I've been in the last month and I have a clear idea of what I need to focus on in order to get to the next level. I would highly recommend Alan to anyone in a leadership role who is feeling overwhelmed and who is trying to reach for some huge goals this year. He is amazing to work with!
